ing units like viscosity, thermal conductivity, and torque. Unlike basic converters, it features animated scale visualizations, real-time formula display, batch conversion, and a keyboard-first command palette.\"}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Unit Converter\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use NIST-sourced factors for engineering work\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use NIST-sourced factors for engineering work\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Every conversion factor in the tool comes from NIST reference data or published engineering tables. For lab reports or design calculations, this matters — internet-scraped factors often round at the third decimal and accumulate error across multi-step conversions.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Switch precision based on context\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border bord